            "answer_text": "To create a fully-functioning contact center, many companies choose contact center automation - and rightly so. With many communication channels available to customers, running a successful contact center is not easy. That\u2019s precisely when automation comes in - to streamline time-consuming tasks like manual data input or constant switching between different communication tools.  The exact benefits of contact center automation often depend on software providers. LiveAgent, for example, combines excellent live chat, ticketing, and automation that allow you to run a successful contact center and provide exceptional support to our customers. ",
